<subSubSection id="C3796513FFECFFF0FF44FC1CFDE814CE" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="8BDC3698FFECFFF0FF44FC1CFDE814CE" blockId="4.[170,795,901,1187]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
<emphasis id="B917EA8AFFECFFF0FF44FC1CFEFA13F3" bold="true" box="[170,296,901,926]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Type data:</emphasis>
This species was described based on a single male specimen (
<figureCitation id="13582A1DFFECFFF0FE6BFC3FFE2413D2" box="[389,502,934,959]" captionStart="Figure 1" captionStartId="3.[94,153,725,750]" captionTargetBox="[94,1401,204,695]" captionTargetId="figure-1@3.[94,1417,204,695]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="Figure 1. Centrispocograndensis Schrottky,1902 (holotype male).(A) Head,frontal view (scale bar: 2 mm).(B) Habitus,dorsal view (scale bar: 5 mm)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4614960" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4614960/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Figs. 1A, B</figureCitation>
) collected in Poço Grande, an old farm near the city of Juquiá (
<bibRefCitation id="EFF24B69FFECFFF0FDA2FC5EFD0D138D" author="Moure, J. S." box="[588,735,967,992]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" pagination="159 - 166" refId="ref4504" refString="Moure, J. S. 2002. Duas especies novas de Centris Fabricius do Peru e notas sobre duas outras de Sao Paulo, esquecidas desde a sua descricao (Hymenoptera, Apoidea, Anthophoridae). Revista Brasileira de Zoologia, 19 (2): 159 - 166. DOI" type="journal article" year="2002">Moure, 2002</bibRefCitation>
). The 
<typeStatus id="54D8883AFFECFFF0FF44FC7EFEDD146D" box="[170,271,999,1024]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">holotype</typeStatus>
is currently housed at 
<collectionCode id="ED72AE5DFFECFFF0FDE0FC7EFD9C146D" box="[526,590,999,1024]" country="Brazil" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/9yp6-zxp9" name="Sao Paulo, Museu de Zoologia da Universidade de Sao Paulo" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" type="Museum">MZSP</collectionCode>
and it has the following data label: [black rimmed] 
<taxonomicName id="4C634D1BFFECFFF0FDCFFB91FCC8144C" authorityName="Schrottky" authorityYear="1902" box="[545,794,1032,1057]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pocograndensis">
<emphasis id="B917EA8AFFECFFF0FDCFFB91FCC8144C" box="[545,794,1032,1057]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Centris poÇograndensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Shrottky 
<specimenCount id="9D65FD11FFECFFF0FEFEFBB0FEF1142D" box="[272,291,1065,1088]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" type="male">♂</specimenCount>
Poço Grande 
<collectingCountry id="F3747608FFECFFF0FE2DFBB1FE2C142C" box="[451,510,1064,1089]" name="Brazil" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Brasil</collectingCountry>
[handwritten]\ [red label with black rim] 
<emphasis id="B917EA8AFFECFFF0FE8DFBD0FD7C140F" box="[355,686,1097,1122]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
Melanocentris 
<taxonomicName id="4C634D1BFFECFFF0FDEAFBD0FD7C140F" authorityName="Schrottky" authorityYear="1902" box="[516,686,1097,1122]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pocograndensis">poÇograndensis</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
(Schr.) 
<specimenCount id="9D65FD11FFECFFF0FCE9FBD0FCC8140D" box="[775,794,1097,1120]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" type="male">♂</specimenCount>
[handwritten] P. Moure det [printed] 1945 [handwritten] Ducke det. 15. Unico! [handwritten].
</paragraph>
